data.description: 3 bed, 2 bath Home on large, level lot with excellent, open floor plan, two very large living areas, the front one anchored by a fireplace and the secondary space opens up to the nice screened-in back porch with a Gazebo. Also, both living areas have built-ins for ample extra storage. New interior paint and new LVP flooring throughout;  tile in kitchen and baths, the formal dining room can also be a 4th bedroom or office. 12x20 Shop building in the back for extra storage. Separate laundry with built-ins. Agents see Confidential remarks for additional information including recent Contractor repairs/improvements.
